{
  "stem": "13469.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was quite agreeable to receiving it, so I sent it back and said, yes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the 11th of November.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You won't hear anything else now, and you might get it and you might not get it, until the list is published.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the day before the list is published, the 30th-- we were not allowed to tell anybody about it, so we didn't tell anybody, especially not our kids.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Corinne was the only one who knew about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very difficult not to tell anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the 30th of December then, the press photographers rang up, so I knew I was in the list and we had all these conversations, which led to Belsen kind of thing and then we had the list.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we heard nothing again kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually later on we had another letter saying there was an investiture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't understand all these words, had to look it all up, and lots of congratulations from all kinds of people I've never heard of.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this investiture, and it says, you're commanded to be at Buckingham Palace-- I can't remember the exact words, because I don't talk in those sort of words-- on such a such a day.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found out later on that you couldn't write back saying that you had a meeting that day or you were abroad or on holiday, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were commanded to be there and that was it and you had to be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you were allowed to bring with you-- what it amounted to was one wife of your own and two children of your own.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
